Package ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.services

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataDispatcher.CANDataListener
    CAN Data Listener interface that every tag that wants to listen for CAN messages should implement.
    DataDispatcher.ModuleDataListener
    Module Data Listener interface that every tag that wants to listen for module messages should implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BroadcastMessage
    Broadcast Message Indicates the fields of the messages going to any tag in need of can information.
    DataDispatcher
    Data Dispatcher The Data Dispatcher receives raw OSC data from the Socket Client and manage the listener for each message type.
    ModuleMessage
    Module Message Indicates the fields of the messages going to any tag in need of module information.
    OronosXmlParser
    Oronos Xml Parser This parser is specifically targeting Oronos rocket xml files.
    RestHttpWrapper
    Rest Http Wrapper Singleton Rest Http Wrapper that is the entry and departure point for any rest/http communication with the server.
    RestHttpWrapper.JSONPostRequestVoidResponse
    Class containing a template of a Json POST Request
    SocketClient
    Socket Client Singleton Datagram Sockets for asynchronous reception of UDP packets.
